text: Daniel Kehr (26 June 1882 - 18 July 1948) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1882 births Category:1948 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:People from Elbeuf
